{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals/task-15","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbao izgovor nosne završnice i slogove.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">üan</span> počinje sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ü</span> poslednjim, koji se izgovara oblikovanjem usana kao da kažete <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span> (savijeno), ali postavljanjem jezika kao da kažete <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span>.</p>\n<p>Da bi izgovorio <span class=\"highlighted-text\">üan</span>, počnite sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ü</span>, zatim otvorite usta malo sa kratkim zvukom kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, i završite s nosom dodirivanjem vrh jezika iza gornjih zuba za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">n</span>.</p>\n<p>Važno je zadržati oblik savijenih usana na početku. Ne izgovarajte ga kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">uan</span>.</p>\n<p>Kada se spoji sa početnim konsonantima <span class=\"highlighted-text\">j</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">q</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">x</span>, dve tačke iznad <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ü</span> se uklanjaju, ali izgovor ostaje kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">üan</span>.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">üan</span> po slogovima, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">xuan</span> u različitim tonovima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Slovo</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">xuān</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">宣</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">xuán</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">玄</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">xuǎn</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">选</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">xuàn</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">炫</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals/task-15"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"cafe.png","characters":[{"character":"Li Hong","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_nasal_finals.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":241.68,"finishTimestamp":258.92},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.8,"dialogue":{"text":"üan","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":3.44,"finishTime":4.27,"dialogue":{"text":"juan","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":5.62,"finishTime":6.54,"dialogue":{"text":"quan","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.99,"finishTime":8.97,"dialogue":{"text":"xuan","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":10.57,"finishTime":11.42,"dialogue":{"text":"xuān","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":12.45,"finishTime":13.42,"dialogue":{"text":"xuán","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":14.67,"finishTime":15.72,"dialogue":{"text":"xuǎn","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":16.9,"finish